General.Name: Scandinavian Medical Solutions AS
General.Description: Scandinavian Medical Solutions A/S deals in medical imaging equipment worldwide. It offers equipment in the categories of CATH lab, CT, linear accelerator, mammography, PET/CT, SPECT/CT, X-ray, ultrasound, MRI, GAMMA/SPECT, C-arm, mobile X-ray, R/F, DEXA, and others, as well as provides CT, MRI, CATH lab, X-ray, MAMMO, PET/CT, and C-arm parts. The company also provides equipment rental and technical services. It serves hospitals, medical clinics, and distributors. The company was incorporated in 2018 and is based in Aalborg, Denmark.
